video.title: The Legend of White Snake
video.synopsis: In this new take on a classic tale, an ancient snake spirit transforms into a beautiful woman and falls in love with a doctor unaware of her true form.

episodes.synopsis: On a quest to understand humanity, Bai Suzhen starts off by challenging the expertise of physician Xu Xian but finds a rival named Qing ready for her.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: After Bai ponders an intervention to heal a strangely sick mother, a noble decision by Xu captures her attention.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Chaos erupts at the Lantern Festival, forcing Bai to defy the heavens. Meanwhile, fighting monk Fahai finds out why the city's children are missing.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: With an assist from an old friend named Jingsong, Bai attempts to find the missing children and learns the truth about the powerful culprit.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Bai fights the powerful culprit with a crew of former adversaries and later tests Xu's integrity when she gets suspicious of the people around him.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: At Xu's family dinner, Bai must act as a mere mortal but faces friction from his longtime admirer, Jin Ruyi.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: While Officer Li Gongfu faces roadblocks in a murder investigation, Jingsong urges Bai to make a life-changing decision for her own well-being.
episodes.title: Episode 7

episodes.synopsis: Xu challenges Bai's decision with a declaration, prompting foxy responses from Ruyi and a new enemy known as Hu Kexin.
episodes.title: Episode 8

episodes.synopsis: Suspicious of Xu's shocking behavior, Jingsong and Qing take action, which leads to a swift response from Bai and a fatal result.
episodes.title: Episode 9

episodes.synopsis: When Bai finds herself caught in a public trial, Xu makes a desperate push to proclaim her innocence.
episodes.title: Episode 10

episodes.synopsis: Jingsong gives Kexin an ultimatum. Bai finally learns the motives behind the murder that shook up Xu's life and the entire city.
episodes.title: Episode 11

episodes.synopsis: When Xu becomes mysteriously ill after the city averts disaster, Bai seeks an antidote that will require tremendous sacrifice.
episodes.title: Episode 12

episodes.synopsis: Bai's major sacrifice forges a new path with Xu but leads to suspicion and displeasure from Officer Li, Ruyi and Jingsong.
episodes.title: Episode 13

episodes.synopsis: After Bai and Xu make their new path official, she discovers a secret regarding his finances and wonders how to respond.
episodes.title: Episode 14

episodes.synopsis: Bai and Xu start an emerging venture that draws an unscrupulous response from Prime Minister Liang, threatening their lives.
episodes.title: Episode 15

episodes.synopsis: As a hunter named Zhang Yutang occupies Qing's mind, Xu and Bai investigate the murky nature of a plague that profits Ruyi's clinic.
episodes.title: Episode 16

episodes.synopsis: Wang Daoling, Ruyi's new physician, must reveal his real identity when Xu and Bai's investigation into the new plague breaks wide open.
episodes.title: Episode 17

episodes.synopsis: When Daoling finally discloses Bai's hidden identity to Ruyi, she plots to keep Xu away from Bai with the assistance of an unaware Fahai.
episodes.title: Episode 18

episodes.synopsis: Ruyi's plan unexpectedly puts Xu's life in jeopardy, pushing Bai to rescue him by searching for a solution in a prohibited land.
episodes.title: Episode 19

episodes.synopsis: Bai finds trouble in the prohibited land and makes a dire plea, but granting this request will change her and Xu's lives forever.
episodes.title: Episode 20

episodes.synopsis: As Xu struggles with his new way of life, Bai makes a firm decision to alleviate his suffering at the expense of her own pain.
episodes.title: Episode 21

episodes.synopsis: Everyone moves forward from Bai's decision except for Xu, who makes a startling revelation that rocks Ruyi to the core.
episodes.title: Episode 22

episodes.synopsis: Xu indulgently dotes on Bai with uncharacteristic behavior, leading her to search for the true reason behind his actions.
episodes.title: Episode 23

episodes.synopsis: Yutang considers an offer to get closer to Qing while Ruyi conspires with Daoling to dispose of Bai using someone from her inner circle.
episodes.title: Episode 24

episodes.synopsis: After an unwanted beggar gives Bai and Xu a surprise for treating him, Qing tries to reveal Ruyi's secret but gets unexpected news about herself.
episodes.title: Episode 25

episodes.synopsis: With growing concerns about Qing's relationship with Yutang, Bai makes an appeal to the immortal Dragon King.
episodes.title: Episode 26

episodes.synopsis: Qing searches for a way to solidify her situation with Yutang, but Fahai's battle with the Mind Demon and Bai's fate could thwart her quest.
episodes.title: Episode 27

episodes.synopsis: While Bai and Xu assist Fahai in his fight against the Mind Demon, Qing must decide if she will forever alter her relationship with Yutang to save him.
episodes.title: Episode 28

episodes.synopsis: Daoling conspires to pit Xu against his close friend while the Mind Demon possesses the body of someone in Xu's inner circle.
episodes.title: Episode 29

episodes.synopsis: After Bai helps Xu understand his past so he can expose Prime Minister Liang, Xu's sister Jiaorong gets good news that Bai knows is secretly tainted.
episodes.title: Episode 30

episodes.synopsis: Certain of Bai's intentions, Xu makes a bold decision that he hopes will preserve the future of his sister Jiarong and her family.
episodes.title: Episode 31

episodes.synopsis: Misunderstandings and powerful truths are revealed when an attempt to save Jiaorong leaves everyone else reeling, especially Bai.
episodes.title: Episode 32

episodes.synopsis: Xu undergoes a dangerous experiment to reverse a tragedy while Qing's vengeful spirit requires a major intervention.
episodes.title: Episode 33

episodes.synopsis: As the truth about the spiritual world spreads through the city, the question of mortality faces Bai and Ruyi with new lives at stake for each of them.
episodes.title: Episode 34

episodes.synopsis: Xu and Fahai consider the only option to stop the Mind Demon from destroying the city, but it requires the ultimate sacrifice -- and hiding it from Bai.
episodes.title: Episode 35

episodes.synopsis: A final effort to stop the Mind Demon requires an intervention that forces heaven and earth to collide, bringing lasting rewards and punishments.
episodes.title: Episode 36
